short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Generate reports automatically for replit.com repositories

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension will generate and populate your clipboard with a valid replit.com report. All you have to do is go to a valid replit.com repl and press the insert key!
